Notice No. CMS-34

March 25, 2002


COMMODITY EXCHANGE, INC.


SWITCH OF GUARANTEE


Please be advised that effective immediately, March 25, 2002, John McNulty

(JMAC-7868) will no longer be guaranteed by Man International, Inc.

However, Mr. McNulty will remain a member guaranteed by Man Financial, Inc.


In connection therewith, notification of any claims against the

aforementioned individual arising out of transactions executed on the

Exchange up to the close of business on March 25, 2002, must be submitted to

the Corporate Secretary's Office within the (10) days.


Inquiries regarding the above should be directed to the Member Services

Department at 212-299-2370.


